715448f-a.title: Manhattan: 126th Street (West) - Lenox Avenue
715448f-a.text:
74-80 West 126th Street, south side, east of Lenox Avenue. The
United Lutheran Church, 74-76 West 126th Street, is at the left.
No. 78, in the centre, is a 12estory frame house. No. 80, on the
right, is the Plantation Club.
1932.
